PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the BEARDY'S & OKEMASIS BAND surrenders for a term of 42 years, some 30.5 hectares of land on Beardy's No. 97 & Okemasis No. 96 Indian Reserve in Saskatchewan, for the purpose of establishing, operating and maintaining a Healing Lodge primarily for federally sentenced Aboriginal men in the custody of Correctional Services.

precis:
Acceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the BEARDY'S & OKEMASIS BAND surrenders
for a term of 42 years, some 30.5 hectares of land on Beardy's No. 97 &
Okemasis No. 96 Indian Reserve in Saskatchewan, for the purpose of
establishing, operating and maintaining a Healing Lodge primarily for
